data.description: This modern and stylishly designed newly built home is situated in a beautiful gated neighborhood, offering privacy and security. As you enter, you will be greeted by a stunning courtyard in the middle of the home, providing a tranquil and peaceful oasis in the heart of your living space.  The home boasts an open and airy floor plan, with sleek and contemporary finishes throughout. The spacious living room, dining area, and kitchen seamlessly flow together, making it perfect for entertaining.The natural light that floods through the large windows and glass doors adds warmth and character to the living space.The bedrooms are located on either side of the home, providing maximum privacy and comfort. The master suite features a large walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom with a luxurious soaking tub and a separate shower. The courtyard is the centerpiece of this beautiful home.  This modern home offers the perfect blend of luxury and comfort, in a safe and secure gated community.
